OL,3,CMeet the eight-year-old with dreams of
OL,4,Cbeing the next Lewis Hamilton
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports sports
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Mike Hall went to meet
OL,8,FJayan Prakash
OL,10,FAn eight-year-old has ambitions of
OL,11,Fbecoming a Formula One champion - just
OL,12,Flike his hero Lewis Hamilton.
OL,14,FJayan Prakash, who lives in
OL,15,FLancashire, is one of brightest young
OL,16,Fstars in the world of , having first
OL,17,Fgot behind the wheel at the young age
OL,18,Fof six.
