OL,3,CMeet the eight-year-old with dreams of
OL,4,Cbeing the next Lewis Hamilton
OL,6,FThe primary school pupil recently won
OL,7,Fthe Global Karting League National
OL,8,FChampionship - his first year of
OL,9,Fcompetitive karting.
OL,11,FHe aspires to follow in the tracks of
OL,12,FBritish driver , who was also an
OL,13,Foutstanding young go-karter and is now
OL,14,Fa seven-time Formula One world
OL,15,Fchampion.
OL,17,F"He never gives up and if something
OL,18,Fgoes wrong he keeps going," Jayan said.
