OL,3,CMeet the eight-year-old with dreams of
OL,4,Cbeing the next Lewis Hamilton
OL,6,FClocking speeds of more than 60 miles
OL,7,Fper hour, Jayan has recorded 20 podium
OL,8,Ffinishes to date and now is now
OL,9,Fsponsored by Porsche.
OL,11,FCharlotte Brown, from Porsche Centre
OL,12,FPreston, said: "We've decided to back
OL,13,FJayan because he's such a talent at
OL,14,Fsuch a young age.
OL,16,F"He's out there competing with kids
OL,17,Ftriple his age and beating them. It's
OL,18,Funreal.
