OL,3,CMeet the eight-year-old with dreams of
OL,4,Cbeing the next Lewis Hamilton
OL,6,F"The speed he's producing and times
OL,7,Fhe's producing. It's everything we
OL,8,Flook for in a talent."
OL,10,FHis dad, Sandeep Prakash, says his son
OL,11,Falways "played with cars in the toy
OL,12,Froom and loved watching Formula One",
OL,13,Fand admits watching from the sidelines
OL,14,Fcan be "scary".
OL,16,F"You have to have faith in what he's
OL,17,Fdoing. He seems to have good control
OL,18,Fon the track," said Sandeep.
